  description: |-
    ### Priorities

    If no custom path was given, and if there are multiple configuration files in the same directory, Mocha will search for ‚Äî and use ‚Äî only one. The priority is:

    1.  `.mocharc.js`
    2.  `.mocharc.yaml`
    3.  `.mocharc.yml`
    4.  `.mocharc.jsonc`
    5.  `.mocharc.json`

